{"tid":1523559,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府回應暴力示威活動","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:05:03.000Z","uid":51469,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f9255240521d01b67a6c67aa8c6f203d415b9350","tid":1523559,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"政府發言人就今日（八月三十一日）在港島和九龍多區的示威活動作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n  今日有大量人士在警方發出反對通知書的情況下，在港島和九龍多區進行未經批准的集結和遊行示威，廣泛堵塞主要道路，導致港島區交通接近癱瘓，嚴重影響緊急服務及市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n  激進示威者在多區與警方對峙，向添馬政府總部、立法會大樓和警察總部以及在不同地方投擲多枚汽油彈，並以腐蝕性液體及磚頭等襲擊警務人員。激進示威者在多處縱火、破壞公物、架起路障、破壞月台幕門等港鐵站設施；軒尼詩道的火勢一度十分猛烈，非常危險。激進示威者這些暴力行為嚴重擾亂社會安寧，對在場執法的警務人員和市民的人身安全構成極大的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n  激進示威者的違法及暴力行為持續升級，罔顧市民大眾的安全，特區政府予以嚴厲譴責，警方亦必定嚴正追究。特區政府將繼續維護法治，並且再次呼籲廣大市民一同向暴力說「不」，讓社會盡快回復秩序。"},{"pid":"6bcb1de1057aad1e7bbd5bd91886d04d398050d5","tid":1523559,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"希望有巴打係樓下補充)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=d4fd3089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump</a><br />\n美國總統 - President Donald.J. Trump <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=77c8b0b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi</a><br />\nNancy Pelosi - Speaker of the House<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gopleader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgopleader&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=e4acf4a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gopleader</a><br />\nKevin McCarthy - GOPLeader<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr\" data-sr-url=